text: Hemicladus fasciatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1991. It is known from Ecuador and Brazil.BioLib.cz - Hemicladus fasciatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1991
title: Hemicladus fasciatus
